{{Quote|It's some kind of musical story or something. The customers probably won't understand this one either, but are we going to pack them in now! Music, singing, dancing!|[[Han Solo]] to [[Chewbacca]], referring to ''Love is Waiting''|<ref name="Han Solo's Revenge">''[[Han Solo's Revenge]]''</ref>}}
'''''Love is Waiting''''' was a [[holograph]]ic drama [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] purchased from his fellow [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Sonniod/Legends|Sonniod]] to replace the dull documentary ''[[Varn, World of Water]]'' at his makeshift [[Holotheater/Legends|holotheater]] on [[Kamar/Legends|Kamar]]. Due to communication difficulties, Solo failed to realize that the desert dwelling [[Kamarian]] [[Kamarian Badlander|Badlanders]] revered water and had set up a religion around his depiction of a water planet. The alternate film caused the [[Cult of Varn]] to riot, forcing Solo and his companions to flee in the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|Millennium Falcon]].

